    <h1>Build Gude - Voyager</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>
<style>[data-colorid=3Dbntc1q51es]{color:#bf2600} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Dbntc1q51es]{color:#ff6640}</style><strong>Introduction =
</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Purpose and scope of the document is to give to you the step by step to =
install process.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Overview of SailPoint IdentityIQ deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Prerequisites </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Hardware and software requirements</p></li>
<li>
<p>Network and security setup</p></li>
<li>
<p>Database configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Installation</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Download Java / JDK</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Create a script folder and update java path </strong></p>
