<p></p>
<p><strong><u>IQ Service Installation:</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Go to Services and stop the IQ service if its running</p></li>
<li>
<p>Go to /tomcat/webapps/identityiq/WEB-INF/bin/win and copy the IQ service=
 folder and extract it.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Login to command Prompt as an administrator and Enter the below command =
to install&nbsp;</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&gt;IQService.exe -i</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Start the service by entering below command</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&gt;IQService.exe -s</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Verify all the AD Application test connections by changing the IQServer =
details, port number to 5051. It should be successful.</p></li>
</ul>
<p></p>
<p><strong><u>Connector Gateway Instation:</u></strong></p></li>
<li>
<p>Login to respective Server&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Download the Latest connector gateway zip from sailpoint compass&nbsp;</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>Place the file in the respective Drive and extract the folder.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Start the Connector gateway by using the below command.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Go to&nbsp; Connector gateway folder through cmd as administrator</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>install.bat 64</p></li>
<li>
<p>go to services and check the connector gateway service and start</p></li=
>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><span data-colorid=3D"bntc1q51es">IdentityIQ installation:</span=
></strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Download latest identityiq.war (8.4)and identityiq-8.4p1.jar and place i=
t to D drive</p></li>
<li>
<p>Extract the identityiq war file using -jar -xvf identityiq.war command</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>Go to WEB-INF/clasess/</p></li>
<li>
<p>Open iiq.proprties and update the datasource user id and pwd</p></li>
<li>
<p>Uncommand SLQ Server settings to update database and connection paramete=
r</p></li>
<li>
<p>Go to WB-INF/database folder</p></li>
<li>
<p>Open the create_identityiq_tables-8.4.SQL Server file and copy all the s=
cripts and paste it in SQL server UI and execute the scripts.</p></li>
<li>
<p>WEB-INF/bin &gt; iiq console and execute ./iiq console -j</p></li>
<li>
<p>Import init.xml</p></li>
<li>
<p>import init-lcm.xml</p></li>
</ol>
<ol start=3D"8">
<li>
<p>Go to identity folder and remove identityiq folder and create a war by c=
ommand jar -cvf identityiq.war *</p></li>
<li>
<p>The above command will create the identityiq.war file</p></li>
<li>
<p>place the war file in to tomcat webapps folder</p></li>
<li>
<p>Restart tomcat server</p></li>
<li>
<p>Access IdentityIQ UI.</p></li>
</ol>
